# Text-to-Audio Converter (T2S)

T2S is a straightforward Python application designed to convert text input into audio files. It leverages text-to-speech synthesis to generate audio from textual content.

## Requirements
- Python
- gTTS (Google Text-to-Speech)

## Usage
1. Run `python manage.py runserver` to initiate the conversion process and generate the audio file.
2. Locate the output audio file in the `output` directory for further use or distribution.

python manage.py collectstatic is needed for initial set up